                                        beginning and at the end).</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </foliation>
                                
                        
                        
                        
                        <collation>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Quires of mostly 16 leaves each (the outer and the
                                        middle leaf of each quire are parchment).</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </collation>
                                
                        
                        
                        
                        <condition>
                           
                           
                           
